## Create Client

> Sample Request

```json
{
  "apiKey": "<%= config.auth %>",
  "identifier": "unique-user-id"
}
```

> 200 Response

```json
{
  "clientId": "579b695decfa11012711875d"
}
```

Creates a client to be used with requests.

### HTTP Request

`POST <%= config.host %>/client/create`

### 200 Response Body

Attribute | Description
--------- | -----------
`clientId` | The ID to be used with requests.
`identifier` | A unique identifier that represents a user in your system.